detecting , formatting ,mounting , using , unmounting  usb drive:
------------------------------------------------------------------
insert usb drive
ls -ltr /dev | tail
fdisk -l

formatting drive:
mkfs.ext2  /dev/sda1 ; (or) mkfs.vfat  /dev/sda1 (or) mkfs.ntfs  /dev/sda1

mount /dev/sda1 /mnt/
umount /dev/sda1 

